OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: Opinion poll
OL,4,Cshows Labour under siege in London
OL,6,FAn opinion poll reveals the scale of
OL,7,Fthe threat to Labour's support in
OL,8,FLondon just days before voters go to
OL,9,Fthe polls in the local elections.
OL,11,FThe survey by More in Common, research
OL,12,Fand polling organisation, shows Labour
OL,13,Fholding their lead in the capital, but
OL,14,Fwith a series of traditional
OL,15,Fstrongholds under siege from Zack
OL,16,FPolanski's Green Party.
OL,18,FReform, meanwhile, are set to make
OL,19,Fgains at the Conservative's expense in
OL,20,Fouter London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
