OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: Opinion poll
OL,4,Cshows Labour under siege in London
OL,6,FMain findings of More in Common poll
OL,8,FLuke Tryl, UK Director at More in
OL,9,FCommon, said: "The 2026 elections are
OL,10,Fset to show that the capital is not
OL,11,Fimmune to the electoral fragmentation
OL,12,Fthat has upended politics across the
OL,13,Fcountry.
OL,15,F"Former Labour strongholds look set to
OL,16,Fsee major Green gains with the
OL,17,Fpotential the party controls or
OL,18,Femerges as the largest party in a
OL,19,Fwhole swathe of inner London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
