FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778155868
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: Opinion poll
OL,4,Cshows Labour under siege in London
OL,6,F"While the Greens advance in Labour's
OL,7,Fheartlands, Reform looks set to do the
OL,8,Fsame in outer-London boroughs such as
OL,9,FBexley that were previously safe for
OL,10,Fthe Conservatives.
OL,12,F"Add in gains from Independents and it
OL,13,Fcould well be that the electoral map
OL,14,Fof London we see on May 8th looks
OL,15,Ftotally unrecognisable to what we have
OL,16,Fbecome used to."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
