OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778155868
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: Opinion poll
OL,4,Cshows Labour under siege in London
OL,6,FMore in Common's poll suggests
OL,7,FLabour's vote share has fallen 15
OL,8,Fpoints in London since the 2024
OL,9,FGeneral Election, the Conservatives
OL,10,Fare down four points, and the combined
OL,11,Fvote of the two traditional parties
OL,12,Fhas fallen by 19 points.
OL,14,FThat support has been seized almost
OL,15,Fentirely by insurgent parties: The
OL,16,FGreen Party's support has increased by
OL,17,F10 points since 2024, while Reform UK
OL,18,Fare up 6 points.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
