OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: Opinion poll
OL,4,Cshows Labour under siege in London
OL,6,FCouncils Labour previously dominated
OL,7,Fsuch as Hackney, Lewisham, Newham,
OL,8,FIslington and Lambeth are now a two-
OL,9,Fway fight between Labour and the
OL,10,FGreens.
OL,12,FMeanwhile the Conservatives may
OL,13,Fstruggle to regain traditional
OL,14,Fstrongholds such as Westminster and
OL,15,FWandsworth and face an assault from
OL,16,FReform in Havering, Bexley and Bromley.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
