OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: Opinion poll
OL,4,Cshows Labour under siege in London
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats are the only
OL,7,Ftraditional party that look set to
OL,8,Favoid the assault on the traditional
OL,9,Fmainstream, holding comfortable leads
OL,10,Fin their south-west strongholds and
OL,11,Fchallenging Labour in Merton.
